Interface INoItemBlock

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlockMultipart

    public interface INoItemBlock
    Disables item for block (only applied to Hammer Core's multipart block. You need to check it for yourseld or use ModBlocks.registerBlock(net.minecraft.block.Block,java.lang.String))
